posting_body: ['Eden Park Apartments is nestled in the heart of Brooklyn Park, MN and surrounded by award-winning parks, lakes, and trails.', 'We are just 15 minutes to downtown Minneapolis from I-694 and I-35W and less than 3 miles from Shoppes at Arbor Lakes, Crystal Shopping Center (near Bass Lake Road and Broadway Avenue) and plenty of everyday conveniences.', 'You can walk to get coffee at Mad Jacks Sports Cafe, Egg House Cafe, or buy groceries at Fast N Fresh Foods.', '-On-Site Management', '-Fitness Center', '-Clubhouse', '-On-Site Maintenance', '-Package Receiving', '-Flex Rent Payments', '-Controlled Access', '-Pool', '-Sundeck', '-Ceiling Fan', '-Playground', '-High Speed Internet', 'Call:', 'show contact info', '6455 Zane Ave N, Brooklyn Park, MN 55429', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Specials are based on availability and may expire or change at any time.', 'Specials and discounts may not be combined.', 'Rates are subject to change without advance notice.']
